GetSize (script event)
======================

Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type {{{gameclass}}}

Description
-----------

Gets the size of this entity's bounding box.

Usage
-----

*vector* getSize()

Parameters
----------

This script event does not accept parameters.

Examples
--------

` `
`sizeBB = `<font color="#000055">`$my_entity`</font>`.`<font color="#ff0000">`getSize`</font><font color="#000000">`(`</font><font color="#000000">`)`</font>`;`

Notes
-----

This script returns the size of this entity's bounding box as a vector.


